Small and white
小而白

977
01:25:26,554 --> 01:25:29,910
Clean and bright
洁而亮

978
01:25:30,158 --> 01:25:32,991
You look happy...
遇见我时

979
01:25:33,194 --> 01:25:37,016
...to meet me
多欢悦

980
01:25:37,298 --> 01:25:39,562
Blossom of snow
雪一般的花儿

981
